terscheidet klipp und klar, wann sie **ich** verwendet und wann **wir**\n\t\t- \"Ich schau mir ein Konzert an\" sagt sie zu Mo, obwohl wir da zusammen hin gehen\n\t\t- \"Ich wünsche mir gemeinsame Planung; ich will da mitgedacht werden.\"\n\t- Diese krasse Trennung interpretiere ich schnell als Egoismus und kenne ich so nicht von mir\n\t\t- Ich misstraue auch meiner Wahrnehmung\n\t- Immerhin hab ich eben mal ausgesprochen, dass ich seit Wochen spüre, wie unzufrieden sie in dieser Beziehung ist",536870916]],["^15",[347,"^1?",1719488236205,536870916]],["^15",[347,"^Z","journals/2024_05_30.md",536870916]],["^15",[348,"^K",1719488236202,536870916]],["^15",[348,"^@",false,536870916]],["^15",[348,"^Y","ambientcg",536870916]],["^15",[348,"^11","ambientCG",536870916]],["^15",[348,"^B",1719488236202,536870916]],["^15",[348,"^;","~u667d4eec-f82b-48a2-8566-516a080fe405",536870916]],["^15",[349,"^K",1719488236202,536870916]],["^15",[349,"^@",false,536870916]],["^15",[349,"^Y","patreon",536870916]],["^15",[349,"^11","Patreon",536870916]],["^15",[349,"^B",1719488236202,536870916]],["^15",[349,"^;","~u667d4eec-651f-4096-8c4e-90b34e5732d1",536870916]],["^15",[350,"^K",1719488236203,536870916]],["^15",[350,"^@",false,536870916]],["^15",[350,"^Y","mail",536870916]],["^15",[350,"^11","Mail",536870916]],["^15",[350,"^B",1719488236203,536870916]],["^15",[350,"^;","~u667d4eec-db81-49d8-b291-30c906be9f52",536870916]],["^15",[351,"^M",true,536870916]],["^15",[351,"^Q","Konsole copy paste Block\ncollapsed:: true",536870916]],["^15",[351,"^O","^1A",536870916]],["^15",[351,"^F",381,536870916]],["^15",[351,"^X",314,536870916]],["^15",[351,"^V",381,536870916]],["^15",[351,"^U",314,536870916]],["^15",[351,"^U",348,536870916]],["^15",[351,"^U",349,536870916]],["^15",[351,"^U",350,536870916]],["^15",[351,"^?",["^ "],536870916]],["^15",[351,"^J",[],536870916]],["^15",[351,"^4",["^ "],536870916]],["^15",[351,"^;","~u667d4eec-b053-47e8-a4d8-7d750a5f8e3f",536870916]],["^15",[352,"^Q","Sie unterscheide